-- Phoenix Solar Says Technology Chief Leaving Board for `Personal Reasons'
-- B y   M i k e   G a v i n
-- 2010-12-14T09:21:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-14/phoenix-solar-says-technology-chief-leaving-board-for-personal-reasons-.html
Phoenix Solar AG said Chief
Technology Officer Manfred Baechler will be leaving the
management board from Dec. 31, 2010, for “personal reasons.”
His responsibilities will be assumed by other board members,
with Chief Executive Officer Andreas Haenel taking over in
particular the chief technology officer role, the company said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mike Gavin at 
 mgavin2@bloomberg.net  